{"tid":2489521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"渠務署58歲承建商員工　辦公室內呼吸困難暈倒後死　23日前打科興","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T04:23:49.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"414e219f5c593c3f1474c482c090fd7c1a759d44","tid":2489521,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新冠疫苗-渠務署58歲承建商員工打科興23日後亡-工作時突呼吸困難暈倒-263079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E6%B8%A0%E5%8B%99%E7%BD%B258%E6%AD%B2%E6%89%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%95%86%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%89%93%E7%A7%91%E8%88%8823%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%99%82%E7%AA%81%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3%E6%9A%88%E5%80%92-263079&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=c804737f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新冠疫苗-渠務署58歲承建商員工打科興23日後亡-工作時突呼吸困難暈倒-263079</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1618127150_5V-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1618127150_5V-1280w.png&h=e4326747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有市民接種科興新冠疫苗後離世。渠務署一名58歲承建商男員工，上周四(8日)晚上在渠務署協調控制中心工作期間，突然感到呼吸困難並暈倒，其後不省人事。在場渠務署同事即時召喚救護車，救護員接報到場後發現他心臟驟停，送明愛醫院急症室後同日晚上證實死亡。死者本身有吸煙習慣，上月16日、即離世前23日，曾在葵涌林士德體育館社區疫苗接種中心，接種科興疫苗，當時未有不適紀錄。"},{"pid":"fba65874d211338f6cdc6dbe28574b130f290842","tid":2489521,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8684b4171e96d41653c4676a3628e040fe28c603","tid":2489521,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"可想而知支那入面因為呢支針死咗幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />武肺死一堆、科興又死一堆"},{"pid":"53f392dcdbc6e2e5c051da08d9c